import React from "react"
import '../../assets/css/Busquedas.css';

import Container from 'react-bootstrap/Container'

import Col from 'react-bootstrap/Col'
import Row from 'react-bootstrap/Row'
import FormBusqueda from './FormBusquedas'
import SearchResult from './SearchResult'


class ComponentBusqueda extends React.Component{

  render(){
    return(
      <Container id='component_busqueda'>
        <Row>
          <Col xs={6}>
              <FormBusqueda />
          </Col>
          <Col md={6}>
            <Card id='search_result_card'>
              <Card.Header > Resultados </Card.Header>
              <Card.Body id='card_body_result_container' >
                holi
              </Card.Body>
            </Card>
          </Col>
        </Row>
      </Container>
    )
  }

}

export default ComponentBusqueda
